{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "第十三章 白玉雕龙\n\n唐花与卫凤娘回到赵公馆，清理入住。唐花独自前往白玉斋，找到书法高手白玉奇，命其模仿赵简笔迹伪造一本日记。白玉奇外号\"通宵快手\"，承诺次日一早完成。唐花取回日记后返程途中，被唐家堡传信骑士拦截。原来赵无忌又被捉回唐家堡，唐傲杀了那三个误事者并放走赵无忌，命唐花将白玉雕龙计划延后两天，待赵无忌抵达后再执行。唐花将日记藏入白玉雕龙机关内，放进赵简书房暗室。两天后，他带卫凤娘进入书房，假装发现暗格和白玉雕龙，取出假日记给卫凤娘看。卫凤娘阅读后脸色大变。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "我到外面走走，待会带点小菜回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "好。你不必急。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "你能模仿得出来吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "除了你我之外，保证普天之下没有第三个人看得出来是我写的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "不，我保证有第三个人看得出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "我还没写，你怎么这么肯定的说有人看得出来呢？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "因为是有人叫我拿来的，叫我来的人难道会不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "唐傲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "哦？那你是……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "我叫唐花。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "啊！对不起。怠慢怠慢了！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "别客气，我是奉唐傲的命令来，不是要你照抄这上面的字，而是要仿上面的字体，写一本日记。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "日记？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "是的。所以你必须找到发黄的纸，绝不能让人看出是新纸，要像旧的。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "我明白了，你要我写什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "你什么时候可以完成？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "急吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "愈快愈好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "明天一早。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "明天一早，这么快？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你知道我有个外号吗？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "叫什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "叫通宵快手。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "好，那我明天一早来拿，还有，纸的尺寸不能太大，要能装进这么大的方圆之内。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "一切照办，你明天准时来就好了，保证一点差错也不会出。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_chuan_xin_ren",
      "text": "有急事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_xin_ren",
      "speaker_name": "传信人",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_chuan_xin_ren",
      "text": "说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_xin_ren",
      "speaker_name": "传信人",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "唐公子请你把白玉雕龙的计划延后两天执行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_chuan_xin_ren",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_xin_ren",
      "speaker_name": "传信人",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "因为有几个不识相的人，又把赵无忌捉回唐家堡去，想领钱立功。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_xin_ren",
      "speaker_name": "传信人",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "唐公子已经把那三个误事的人杀了，也把赵无忌放走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_chuan_xin_ren",
      "text": "那为什么还要把计划延后？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_xin_ren",
      "speaker_name": "传信人",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "我是日以继夜赶快马而来，但赵无忌却是缓缓而来，唐公子说怕万一计划执行太早，那姓卫的女子等不及告诉赵无忌，就告诉了别的大风堂的人，那就不好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_chuan_xin_ren",
      "text": "我知道了，你估计赵无忌什么时候可以回到这里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_xin_ren",
      "speaker_name": "传信人",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "两天以后的黄昏时分应该可以到达。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_chuan_xin_ren",
      "text": "好，那我就晚两天才执行，你回去覆命，请他们放心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "这么漂亮的一条白玉雕龙，怪不得要放在这个暗格里面来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "是呀，不过，这外面也有很多精品，不亚于这个雕龙，为什么偏偏要摆这个呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "对呀，为什么？难道还有别的秘密？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "说不定哦。我来检查看看。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "我不要看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "这么机密的东西，我还是不看的好。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "还是看看比较好，收藏得这么秘密的东西，一定是记录着很重要的事，怎么能不看呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你看好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "我看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "是呀，你看我看还不是一样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "怎么啦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "太可怕了，你自己看好了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    }
